data.description: Beautiful home in a desirable quaint neighborhood. A home where families want to get together, warm, cozy and comforting. Meticulously maintained with attention to every detail. Dramatic foyer entry with hardwood flooring and a spindled curved staircase. Formal Living and Dining Room, great for entertaining. Fabulous large kitchen with beautiful hardwood flooring, and an island breakfast bar, Family Room with a Cozy fireplace. Extra large master bedroom with huge walk-in closet.  4 Generous sized bedrooms. Fully finished and carpeted basement. Laundry on main floor. Backyard is fenced providing privacy with a tiered deck and a stamped concrete patio. There isn't a Home owners association All you need to do is move in.
